<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MISSILE-MENACE-N.KOREA-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
MORE STICKS, FEWER CARROTS FOR NASTY KIM JONG II  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
