<P>
   &UR; TEXTURES COULD MAKE THE WEB MORE FUN &LR;  _ Shoppers on the
Internet will soon be able to experience the ability to `touch'
items pictured on the Net. A Californian company has created a
motorised computer mouse that enables the computer user to feel the
texture of a pair of corduroy jeans or feel what it's like to
test-drive a car. By Catherine Zandonella. 450 words. Slugged:
BC-WEB-TEXTURES-(NEW-SCIENTIST)-NYTSF) &QL;
</P>
