<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-09 13:22 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4389 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ONADVERTISING-COLUMN &LR;      07-09 0774
