<HEADLINE>
TOO MANY COOKING SHOWS SPOIL TELEVISION 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: Filed in entertainment, ``e,'' and food, ``d,'' categories(  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By KEN ALEXANDER  
 c.1999 San Francisco Examiner  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LAFAYETTE, Calif. _ There are scads of things to get irritated
about these days. I'm the irritable type, so selecting one is no
problem, be it the government, school shootings, pollution, ethnic
cleansing, the plight of the poor or any of dozens of festering sit
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-07-09-99 1346EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
