</P>
<P>
   &QR;  June 14 _ Thirty adolescent students are taken to a hospital
in Ghent after drinking canned Cokes from a machine at a school in
nearby Lochristi. The Belgian government orders all Coca-Cola
products off store shelves and stops production at bottling plants
