<SLUG> BC-HILLARY-CLINTON-1STLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
  
 HILLARY CLINTON WRAPS UP FIRST BIG FORAY IN NEW YORK   (EDs: FIXES
lede, changing an to a)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By STEWART M. POWELL  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
