to figures compiled by the Consumer Electronics Manufacturers
Association. DVD Video experienced 300 percent growth in second
quarter 1999, shipping more than 730,000 hardware units compared to
170,000 in the second quarter 1998. By Dave McNary. (Will move in
the ``f'' financial news file.)
