</P>
<P>
   MARKET (New York) _ For the second consecutive Friday, the stock
market finished the week with a hat trick, as all the three major
indexes reached new highs. Bond prices ended slightly lower as Ford
Motor Co. completed the biggest corporate bond issue ever. By
Jonathan Fuerbringer.
</P>
