</P>
<P>
   (NYT19) MUZAFFARABAD, Kashmir -- July 9, 1999 -- KASHMIR, 07-09
-- Mourners carrying their war dead Thursday in Muzaffarabad, where
hatred of India, and suspicion of Pakistani and American officials,
intertwine. The young men were blown apart in battle by artillery
fire a few miles from here. Though they were not well known, 2,000
