</P>
<P>
   (NYT18) CAMBRIDGE, Mass. -- July 8, 1999 -- LEGAL-SCHOLARS,
07-08 -- Prof. Charles J. Ogletree Jr. in his office at Harvard Law
School where he teaches. Ogletree and A. Leon Higginbotham Jr., who
