bid as Republican and conservative groups, from Alabama to New
Hampshire, use her candidacy to raise millions of dollars. The
placards at right make reference to New York City Mayor Rudolph
Giuliani, a Republican, who is also exploring a run for the Senate.
(Keith Meyers/New York Times Photo)
</P>
